item.title: My "RSIA"
item.dc:creator: @zyle1992 Zymus
item.description:
@zyle1992 wrote:

[quote=“slogieftw, post:1, topic:324502”]OFF TOPIC-
W0000t finished ma new server, and just got back from vacation
Had a great time, Went to cubaa

OFF-ish ON-ish TOPIC-
Hey guys, i need some helpp
i’ve just finished my “RSIA” server. (RuneScape Insane Asylum)
This server is epicly epic.
I even coded a straight jacket into it, but it took a while
cause’ i was using Zezinascape base o-o

ON TOPIC-
I have finished it all, but i have a slight problem,
I uh… kinda forgot to DL JDK 6.0 and i can’t DL cause’
it always says “Error, Exiting installation. Try again later”
So, if anyone could help me, That would be great.
i’m looking for somone trustworthy,
i would prefer senior mems and up, but w.e,
If you will help me reply and i’ll send you dl link for the server
so you can compile :]

Thanks.

-Jamie (SlogieFtw)[/quote]

Inconsistencies:

  1. Adding a straight jacket is client side, not server side.
  2. If you’re using the same computer, you already have jdk 6. If all else fails, uninstall the jdk and re install it.

Honest Opinion: Just an attempt the get help, but trying to do it in a nonchalant way so you don’t sound like an idiot.
